valid or maybe a little
bit left of center

00:52:42.740 --> 00:52:46.220
right down to physical
stuff you've heard.

00:52:46.220 --> 00:52:47.810
So the floor,
guys, is now really

00:52:47.810 --> 00:52:50.355
